# Jest needs Node's vm modules API to require() ESM-only dev dependencies
# (axios-cookiejar-support v6+ and its agent-base dependency). Requires
# Node >= 24.9 (see engines). npm exports node-options as NODE_OPTIONS for
# every lifecycle script, so all jest invocations pick it up; ${NODE_OPTIONS?}
# preserves any externally set NODE_OPTIONS (empty string when unset).
node-options="${NODE_OPTIONS?} --experimental-vm-modules"
